## Constitution IX: Repo First, MCP Second (NON-NEGOTIABLE)

**NEVER seek from the database what you can get from the repo.**

- Dataplatform SSDT repo (`Dataplatform\SynapseSQLPool1\sql_dp_prod_we\`) has ALL DDLs for Synapse objects (343 tables, 126 SPs, 22 views for DWH_dbo)
- DB_Schema SSDT repo has ALL production DDLs and upstream wikis
- Synapse MCP is ONLY for live data queries (Phases 2-3: `SELECT TOP N`, `COUNT(*)`, `GROUP BY`)
- See `.cursor/rules/semantic-layer-core/repo-first-access.mdc` for full enforcement table
